  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>ReadCounterValue</TypeRef> method attempts to read the captured counter value.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[SuccessToken ReadCounterValue(uint32_t& counterValue) const;]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Argument list">
      <ArgumentList>
        <ArgumentListEntry Type="uint32_t" Name="counterValue">
          The variable that receives the captured counter value.
        </ArgumentListEntry>
      </ArgumentList>
    </SubSection>
    <SubSection Title="Return value">
      <ReturnValue Type="SuccessToken">
        True if the operation succeeded, false otherwise. An assertion will be raised in debug builds if the result is not tested.
      </ReturnValue>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
